spec_data.Name: perl-CPAN-Common-Index
spec_data.Description:
This module provides a common library for working with a variety of CPAN
index services. It is intentionally minimalist, trying to use as few non-
core modules as possible.
spec_data.Signature: RSA/SHA256, Fri 01 Sep 2017 08:28:48 AM EDT, Key ID f55e7430f5282ee4
spec_data.Summary: Common library for searching CPAN modules, authors and distributions
